title: Waada Raha (Aishwarya Rai Remixed)
description:
Waada Raha (Aishwarya Rai Remixed)

This is a remixed version of the song "Waada Raha" from the Hindi Movie "Khakee".

This is not a remix version in a true sense! In the movie, we have the video song 

"Waada Raha" of duration 02:27, while in Audio CD, the track "Waada Raha" is present

for a duration of around 04:13.

In this video clip, somebody has taken the audio track and mixed it with Aishwarya's video clips from her different video songs...

Anyway, I liked it, hoping you will also like it....
